            <CodePage>          (Required) The code page associated with these fonts. See http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/goglobal/bb964654.aspx.
                                If an RSC font is not specifically configured in this file, it is assumed to use your ACP (Active Code Page).
                                At the time of this writing, should be one of:
